body:
Select  R.ITRaporIslemID, R.RaporID, R.RaporAdi, M.ModulAdi, MAG.ModulAltGrupKodu, NIG.NavItemGroupName, S.ScreenCaption, S.ScreenID
From    IT15_ObjectsRaporIslemleri R
        Inner Join IT15_Screens S On S.ITObjectID = R.ITObjectID
        Left Join IT15_NavItemGroups NIG On NIG.NavItemGroupID = S.NavItemGroupID
        Inner Join IT15_ModulAltGruplari MAG On MAG.ModulAltGrupID = S.ModulAltGrupID
        Inner Join IT15_Moduller M On M.ModulID = MAG.ModulID
Where   R.RaporID = 2005
Go
